<br>
I don't know how the general Skald community feels but has anyone ever suggested that Skald's be given the ability to use Spear styles?<br>
<br>
How difficult would it be for Mythic to add this style to Skalds repetoire? Considering that we gain no benefit from 1hdr / shield combo, except in base percentage.<br>
